            "children": [
              {
                "id": "rule_1",
                "type": "rule",
                "content": {
                  "text": "**expo-audio-stream** is a comprehensive audio processing monorepo for React Native and Expo applications. It provides real-time audio recording, analysis, visualization, and AI-powered processing capabilities across iOS, Android, and web platforms.",
                  "originalHeader": "Repository Overview"
                },
                "metadata": {
                  "strength": "SHOULD",
                  "format": "Paragraph",
                  "line_start": 6,
                  "line_end": 6
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "rule_2",
                "type": "rule",
                "content": {
                  "text": "- **`@siteed/expo-audio-studio`** - Main audio processing library with dual-stream recording, device management, and format conversion\n- **`@siteed/expo-audio-ui`** - React Native Skia-based audio visualization components (waveforms, spectrograms)\n- **`@siteed/react-native-essentia`** - Advanced audio analysis using Essentia (feature extraction, classification)\n- **`@siteed/sherpa-onnx.rn`** - Speech-to-text and text-to-speech capabilities (development)",
                  "originalHeader": "Core Packages"
                },
                "metadata": {
                  "strength": "SHOULD",
                  "format": "ListItem",
                  "line_start": 9,
                  "line_end": 12
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "rule_3",
                "type": "rule",
                "content": {
                  "text": "- **`apps/playground`** - Full-featured demo app showcasing all capabilities\n- **`apps/minimal`** - Simple integration example\n- **`apps/essentia-demo`** - Audio analysis demonstrations",
                  "originalHeader": "Applications"
                },
                "metadata": {
                  "strength": "SHOULD",
                  "format": "ListItem",
                  "line_start": 15,
                  "line_end": 17
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "rule_4",
                "type": "rule",
                "content": {
                  "text": "Standard: **iPhone 16 Pro Max** \u2014 use `yarn setup:ios-simulator` for consistent setup.",
                  "originalHeader": "iOS Simulator"
                },
                "metadata": {
                  "strength": "SHOULD",
